{"word":"H4550 - מַסַּע - maççaʻ - mas-sah' - Journey","slug":"H4550","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַסַּע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>maççaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mas-sah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Journey"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E1;&#x05BC;&#x05E2; - massa&#x201B;</b> - <i>mas-sah</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5265\">H5265</a>; a <i>departure</i> (from <i>striking</i> the tents), that is, march (not necessarily a single day&rsquo;s travel); by implication a <i>station</i> (or point of <i>departure</i>): - journey (-ing)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4551\">H4551</a>, <a href=\"#/H5265\">H5265</a>"}]}